Version 0.4:
 * Added support for Player 2.1.X;
 * Added support for LEDs. Blinkenlight interface in Player 2.1.X and opaque
   interface in Player 2.0.X;
 * Added compatibility with the new e-puck cameras (PO6030K);
 * The image grabbed from camera is delivered always in correct orientation.

Version 0.3:
 * Added the camera interface.
 * Improved the synchronization between e-puck and PC, saving CPU processing.
 * Reorganized the documentation files in general.

Version 0.2:
 * Initial release.
 * Implemented position2d and ir interfaces.
